<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Project Shared Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #4CAF50;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 10px 20px;
    }
    .content .project-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Project Shared with You!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>

      <p>{{sharedBy}} has shared a project with you on our platform. Below are the details of the shared project:</p>

      <div class="project-details">
        <strong>Project Name:</strong> {{projectName}}<br>
        <strong>Shared By:</strong> {{sharedBy}}
      </div>

      <p>You can view and collaborate on this project by clicking the link below:</p>

      <a href="{{projectLink}}" class="cta-button">View Project</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      <p>Thank you for using our platform!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
